      <a href="mailto:info@yspcollective.com">info@yspcollective.com</a><br>
      Resposta em até 2 dias úteis.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- ENGLISH -->
  <div class="policy-lang" id="lang-en">

    <div class="highlight-box">
      <p>Something not right with your order? We have 14 days to sort it. Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@yspcollective.com">info@yspcollective.com</a> and we'll take care of everything.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Right of Withdrawal</h2>
    <p>Under Portuguese Decree-Law No. 24/2014 (implementing EU Directive 2011/83/EU on consumer rights), you have the right to withdraw from your purchase within <strong>14 calendar days</strong> of receiving your order, without giving any reason.</p>
    <p>To exercise this right, notify us of your decision to withdraw by email at <a href="mailto:info@yspcollective.com">info@yspcollective.com</a> before the 14-day period expires.</p>

    <h2>2. Return Conditions</h2>
    <p>For a return to be accepted, products must be returned:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>In their original condition — <strong>unused, sealed, with all original packaging intact</strong>.</li>
      <li>With proof of purchase (order number or receipt).</li>
      <li>Within 14 days of notifying us of your withdrawal.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Exceptions:</strong> Under Art. 17(1)(e) of Decree-Law No. 24/2014, the right of withdrawal does not apply to sealed goods which are not suitable for return due to health protection or hygiene reasons, where the seal has been broken after delivery. This includes fragrances, cosmetics and skincare products whose protective seal has been opened.</p>

    <h2>3. Defective or Incorrect Products</h2>
    <p>If you received a defective, damaged or incorrect product, you are entitled to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Repair or replacement of the product, at no cost to you;</li>
      <li>A proportional price reduction;</li>
      <li>Cancellation of the contract with a full refund.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>In these cases, return shipping costs are our responsibility. Please contact us within <strong>14 days</strong> of receipt to report any issue.</p>

    <h2>4. Returns Process</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Email <a href="mailto:info@yspcollective.com">info@yspcollective.com</a> with your order number, the item(s) to return and the reason.</li>
      <li><strong>Step 2:</strong> You will receive return instructions within <strong>2 business days</strong>.</li>
      <li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Send the item(s) securely packaged to the address provided.</li>
      <li><strong>Step 4:</strong> Once received and inspected, your refund will be processed within <strong>14 days</strong>.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Refunds</h2>
    <p>Refunds are issued via the same payment method used for the original purchase, unless expressly agreed otherwise. The refund includes the product price and original delivery costs (except where you chose a more expensive delivery option than the standard one).</p>
    <p>We may withhold the refund until we receive the returned goods or until you provide proof of dispatch.</p>

    <h2>6. Return Shipping Costs</h2>
    <p>Except in cases of defective or incorrectly sent products, return shipping costs are the customer's responsibility.</p>

    <h2>7. Legal Guarantee</h2>
    <p>Under Portuguese Decree-Law No. 84/2021 (implementing EU Directive 2019/771), all goods sold carry a <strong>3-year legal conformity guarantee</strong> from the date of delivery. During the first 12 months, any lack of conformity is presumed to have existed at the time of delivery.</p>

    <h2>8. Complaints</h2>
    <p>Under Portuguese law, you may submit complaints through the <strong>Electronic Complaints Book</strong> at <a href="https://www.livroreclamacoes.pt" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.livroreclamacoes.pt</a>.</p>
    <p>For alternative dispute resolution, you may contact the competent Consumer Arbitration Centre for your area, or use the European online dispute resolution platform: <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr</a>.</p>

    <div class="policy-contact-box">
      <p><strong>Returns and complaints:</strong><br>
      YSP Collective · Portugal, European Union<br>
      <a href="mailto:info@yspcollective.com">info@yspcollective.com</a><br>
      Response within 2 business days.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
